(340, 'en', 'theme option-tree', 'a4eb60e8b535f784d3f785dba98dcc93', 'The ID field is a unique alphanumeric key used to differentiate each theme option (underscores are acceptable). Also, the plugin will change all text you write in this field to lowercase and replace spaces and special characters with an underscore automatically.', 0),
(341, 'en', 'theme option-tree', 'a1fa27779242b4902f7ae3bdd5c6d508', 'Type', 0),
(342, 'en', 'theme option-tree', '2ed0b343f1ff96f8962751fd43524d0d', 'You are required to choose one of the supported option types when creating a new option. Here is a list of the available option types. For more information about each type click the <code>Option Types</code> tab to the left.', 0),
(343, 'en', 'theme option-tree', 'e86f260738befdaf38d5cc409b2172a7', 'Enter a detailed description for the users to read on the Theme Options page, HTML is allowed. This is also where you enter content for both the Textblock & Textblock Titled option types.', 0),
