(464, 'en', 'theme option-tree', '019f557dfe14875ad0cdffc4b8eab910', 'The next two examples demonstrate how to use the <strong>Measurement</strong> option type. The Measurement option type is an array with two key/value pairs. The first is the value of measurement and the second is the unit of measurement.', 0),
