5:{s:4:"data";s:337:"Today we are happy to announce that we have another 5 themes to add to our compatibility list. The themes are Real homes, Brooklyn, Interio, Jupiter and ProPhoto. If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here: Multilingual Ready Themes Multilingual Ready Plugins [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"Dominykas";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5291:"<p>Today we are happy to announce that we have another 5 themes to add to our compatibility list. The themes are <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/real-homes-wordpress-real-estate-theme/5373914" target="_blank">Real homes</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/brooklyn-creative-one-page-multipurpose-theme/6221179" target="_blank">Brooklyn</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/interio-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/4616897" target="_blank">Interio</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/jupiter-multipurpose-responsive-theme/5177775" target="_blank">Jupiter</a> and <a href="http://www.prophoto.com/" target="_blank">ProPhoto</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Themes " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Plugins " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Real homes theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/real-homes-wordpress-real-estate-theme/5373914" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/real-homes.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Real homes is designed for real estate related websites. It has nice &amp; clean design and it comes loaded with a good number of features like advanced search, google map with properties markers, simple &amp; grid listing, custom widgets, various templates, easy theme options and easy to use metaboxes.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/real-homes-wordpress-real-estate-theme/5373914" target="_blank">Purchase Real homes</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Brooklyn theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/brooklyn-creative-one-page-multipurpose-theme/6221179" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/brooklyn.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Brooklyn is a simple theme with a clean layout. Some features of Brooklyn are: shortcode builder, 3 different portfolio styles, parallax background support and 6 different header styles.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/brooklyn-creative-one-page-multipurpose-theme/6221179" target="_blank">Purchase Brooklyn</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Interio theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/interio-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/4616897" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/interio.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Interio is a clean, modern design multipurpose WordPress theme which can be used for any type of website. It comes with a number of options so you can modify layout, styling, colors and fonts directly from within the backend.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/interio-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/4616897" target="_blank">Purchase Interio</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Jupiter theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/jupiter-multipurpose-responsive-theme/5177775" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/jupiter.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Jupiter is a clean, flexible, responsive and retina ready WordPress theme. You can modify options and settings via Jupiters robust Admin Panel. Change your site colors and control your layout with point and click options. Choose from different layouts and templates on a page-by-page basis or start creating a whole new layout.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/jupiter-multipurpose-resp