nsive-flat-bootstrap-wordpress-theme/6184186" target="_blank">Flati</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/unreal-estate-real-estate-wordpress-theme/5633361" target="_blank">UnrealEstate</a> and <a href="http://www.cssigniter.com/club88/" target="_blank">Club88</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Themes " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Plugins " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Qualia theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/qualia-flexible-multipurpose-theme/5767606" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/qualia.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Qualia is a multi-purpose theme suitable for business, corporate, portfolio and blog. Brand new admin panel with features like color sets, text typography, google fonts and shortcodes.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/qualia-flexible-multipurpose-theme/5767606" target="_blank">Purchase Qualia</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Karma theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/karma-responsive-modern-clean-wordpress/168737" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/karma.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Karma is a simple theme with a clean layout. This theme is suitable for a brandable site and also for personal blog. It comes with the theme options panel, so its easy to customize.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/karma-responsive-modern-clean-wordpress/168737" target="_blank">Purchase Karma</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">UnrealEstate</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/unreal-estate-real-estate-wordpress-theme/5633361" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/unreal-estate.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Unreal Estate is a responsive real estate theme which allows you to display a good number of properties, search using many criterias and options, view the information in three different ways and communicate with potential buyers.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/unreal-estate-real-estate-wordpress-theme/5633361" target="_blank">Purchase UnrealEstate</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Flati theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/flati-responsive-flat-bootstrap-wordpress-theme/6184186" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/flati.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Flati is a responsive portfolio WordPress Theme which has been built using the Twitter Bootstrap framework. Some features of Flati are: unlimited sidebars, revolution slider, contact form and shortcodes.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/flati-responsive-flat-bootstrap-wordpress-theme/6184186" target="_blank">Purchase Flati</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Club88 theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/club88-premium-music-wordpress-theme/5740471" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692" alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/club88.png" width="590" height="291" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Club88 theme is aimed at clubbers in need for a solution that focuses on what matters most to them. User friendly admin panel allows you to do customizations without knowing any HTML or CSS.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/club88-premium-music-wordpress-theme/5740471" target="_blank">Purchase Club88</a></p>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:84:"http://wpml.org/2013/12/week-compatible-qualia-karma-flati-unrealestate-club88/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"